This Map is a aim map with the textures of aim_ag_texture_city and texture2.
The Map has two building on each side with spawns inside, and when you go outside you are greeted with a maze, and if you go behind spawn you can take a ramp up to a catwalk above. This map has 1 secret. Hint--Check behind the boxes near the tower

-Thank you for all your support
